  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb2 \u0baa\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 10 \u0bae\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bc7\u0bb0 \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "10 hour water cut in some parts of Colombo",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The National Water Supply and Drainage Board has announced that a 10 hour water cut will be imposed in many parts of the Colombo district today (Saturday).",
        "Accordingly, the water cut will be implemented from 10:00 pm on Saturday to 08:00 am on Sunday.",
        "Accordingly, Edul Fort, Purakkottai, Baddegama, Mirihana, Madiwela, Thalapathpitiya, Udahamulla, Embuldeniya, Nugegoda, Bagoda, up to the 7th Mile Pillar and all the crossroads of the High Level Road in the area, including the Nugegoda Junction to the Open University Thus water cut will be implemented in the areas."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "10 hour",
          "label": "TIME"
        }
      ],
